 &QL; 
 &UR; Barbara Cade-Menum &LR; , a Canadian working at Stanford University,
forwards an outraged report from the Edmonton News about
 &UR; Condoleezza Rice &LR; , who the newspaper says is ``repeatedly referred
to as a foreign policy supergenius'' and ``is paid a princely sum
