move not only across the screen on the x and y axes but also in and
out, along the z axis. The PHANTOM was designed and built by
SensAble Technologies. Coupled with a software program called
FreeForm, it may herald an important change in the way human beings
and computers interact. A report. Color art is available. (slugged:
