<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-QUIZZICAL-QADDAFI-RESEND-FISK-INDEPENDENT-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
ODD QUESTIONS ABOUT QADDAFI'S LATEST MISCHIEF  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
