<SLUG> BC-E-THERAPY-NNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
MENTAL HEALTH THERAPY ONLINE HOLDS PROMISE, DANGERS 
</HEADLINE>
   ATTENTION EDITORS: This article from NEWHOUSE NEWS SERVICE for
THURSDAY, Aug. 24, is available as a ``separate-buy.'' For
information about purchasing the article, contact DEBRA WEYDERT of
The New York Times Syndicate at 1-212-499-3401; fax, 732-390-4697;
e-mail: weyded(at)nytimes.com.) 
 ART ADVISORY: With two photos, of Peter Chechele (NNS4) and Joan
Maricle (NNS5). For information about purchasing these photos call
202-383-7824. 
