<DOCNO> NYT20000824.0343 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-24 20:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1448 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-BKC-GOODMAN-ART-900(2     08-24 0973
