Brown at Saks.
</P>
<P>
   PHOTO 5: WOMAN IN FRONT OF PAINTING IN ANIMAL PRINT/AT HOME
</P>
<P>
   ``When your head is erect, your gaze outward and your backbone
is as straight as Mother Nature made possible, you are inviting
others to meet with you on equal terms. Mother was right: Stand Up
Straight! ``
</P>
<P>
   _ Etiquette for Dummies by Sue Fox
</P>
<P>
   SNAKE CHARMER: Matte jersey snakeskin print shirt ($34.50) with
