</P>
<P>
   ``Whether you forget a name, put them in the wrong order or make
any other mistake, some form of introduction is better than none at
all.''
</P>
<P>
   _ Emily Post's Etiquette by Peggy Post
</P>
<P>
   MEET AND GREET: (left to right) Cheetah print blouse ($39.50)
