that's hidden beneath the boulevards, one that creeps adjacent to
the Seine. To experience it, you must descend. Down into the dark
and, later, back up to the City of Light. The Paris Metro, the
catacombs, the sewers ... these are perhaps the most famous sights
of Underground Paris. (Sturrock, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art
